data.description: WOW!! Seller is Motivated and offering 10K to use as you wish, or towards closing costs, and a home warranty with full price offer!! All inspections and repairs are done. All new appliances put in on 10/05/23. New HVAC system put in 2021 A roof tune up in 2021 all valleys were redone. This home has a large yard, over half acre w/dog pen and a great bbq area right outside the newly carpeted sunroom. 3 bedrooms 2 bath, bonus room w/closet which could be 4th bedroom. Master bedroom with attached flex room. Large master bath with double vanities, soaking tub and separate shower. Conveniently located within 30 minutes to post, 1 hour to Raliegh. Close to shopping, restaurants and within 6 miles to HWY 1. Schedule your showing today!!!
